This shows how you can make directly download from Google Drive.

###Step 1:

Copy the shared link from your Google Drive.
Eg.https://drive.google.com/open?id=1bIONsTideFpiTZxcrVuKppZ1SurwH0Dm

Here your file has id and browser is setting it to open.
It must be changed as

###Step 2:
Remove open and add uc?export=download&

https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&id=1bIONsTideFpiTZxcrVuKppZ1SurwH0Dm

It will be downloadble now.
